@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 14

title Application built on top of HTTP

rectangle "Custom Application\n(REST client / RPC stub)" as app
rectangle "HTTP\n(requests & responses)" as http
rectangle "TCP\n(reliable stream)" as tcp
rectangle "IP\n(routing)" as ip

app --> http : uses HTTP as\napplication channel
http --> tcp
tcp --> ip

note right of app
  The programmer ignores
  layers below HTTP.
  E.g., REST API, JSON-RPC
  over HTTP.
end note

note right of http
  Standard methods:
  GET, POST, PUT, DELETE
end note
@enduml
